text: If the two words never shake and hide up. I guess I never understand. Things can be the pain. Is just break up.
If tomorrow never ask for more. Then hold my hands to the walk.
Ten thousands of doors. Be waiting for the sorrow.
No friendship can never be careful. So writing for we say goodbye. We should enjoy and share our tears.
Before two days. I’ve being love you. You think in love to me. You will met a stranger.
Another show good and pass me by for walking on this lonely street.
After two days, we’ll make no reference. Nothing for hello. Nothing to remember.
Remember we looked our hearts and kiss then. And our love lesson that fades away.
